{
  "stem": "21310.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So now-- so they never really caught her and she never-- but he gave him the name of the-- the Zoszak name.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So that was a-- a kind of a close call.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Your parents went to Warsaw?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, that-- they had-- some blackmailers, Polish blackmailers came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother was able to-- to hide my father under-- underground.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He hid.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- and it was early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she threw his clothing also in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the bed was still warm, from-- because my father-- it was early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she had forgotten his gold watch was, like, on a little table next to the bed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And three of these blackmailers came in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they said they're looking for-- they were told that a communist lives here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because at that time, it wasn't-- for the Poles, they-- they wouldn't say a-- a Jew, but a communist.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, that somehow it was more acceptable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so-- so, my mother says, no, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He-- you know, he's not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and so on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then they said to my mother, don't lie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The bed is still warm, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and so they went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there was another trapdoor in the regular cellar from the-- in the kitchen, which wasn't the hole that we dig-- dug out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they went into that cellar to look, two of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One stayed behind and told my mother, look, I know that he's here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I-- I saw the watch, the man's watch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You give me the watch and-- and I come back later for the watch.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you put a newspaper on that watch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And say, you give me that watch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I come later for it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Don't tell the other ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I'm going to get them away from here.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
